Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not good to lack honorifics, kouhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You will call me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Muramasa-senpai"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's with you, suddenly interrupting us,\Nand all this about crushing dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You were a super-popular author\Nwho has sold over 2 million copies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes! Worship me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kagurazaka-san, please tell them\Nhow many copies I've sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muramasa-sensei's total copies sold is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,14.5 million copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fourteen point five...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you have more than 1 million copies' worth\Nof difference in sales, you can say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You said something of the sort, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now let's get to the main topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It seems you are angry, kouhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because my senpai made fun of our dream,\Nand because she said she'd crush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, I said that. And, I carried it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Carried out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The reason why the release date for your recent\Nproject proposal has been delayed by a year
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,is because I intentionally took\Nthe publishing slot away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have been keeping up with your actions\Nby going through Kagurazaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you antagonize me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You, embracing such pointless dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I hate you for getting in the way of my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I'll crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let me say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Losing just once\Nwon't make me give up my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, I'll just keep crushing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, let's settle the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The winner of the Light-novel Tenkaichi Budoukai\Ncan give any order to the loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, Masamune!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I win, I won't let you get in the way\Nof our dream ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I lose, do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I couldn't ask for a better proposition.\NBut are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:02:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Our dream isn't pointless at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I challenge you, Muramasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why'd you get so heated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wasn't there a much better way of handling it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She made fun of our dream.\NI can't ever forgive her for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you have that much determination,\Nwhy are you moping around so depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I put our dream on the line on just my accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For that, I feel guilt towards\NEromanga-sensei... my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know what I should say to Sagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sounds like she's calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought you needed me for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cheater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Was your date fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.35,LeftSign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz45.85\fs25\frx8\fry356\fscx93\fscy80\move(309.167,241.778,300.334,244.445,1,2337)}On a date with Izumi Masamune-sensei right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.35,LeftSign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz45.85\fs35\frx12\fry354\move(97.167,310.222,72.434,318.222,1,2420)}Yamada Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be from that time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course that's one of Elf's jokes. I told you\NI was heading to the editorial office with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san, you can't go on dates\Nwith girls for the rest of your life. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-The rest of my life, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. The rest of your life. Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come up here right away\Nafter you came home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was worried about\Nwhat happened to our work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...I feel guilt against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That guy. He says he loves his younger sister,\Nbut doesn't understand her one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I put our dream on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not something\NI can decide on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides, there might have been\Nanother way to go about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Another way? You're fine\Nwith someone making fun of our dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you thinking about losing\Nbefore you even try?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That guy who laughed at our dream\Nis our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's take this on together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:06:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're right. If the two of us are together,\N10 million copies won't even be an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll take this on together, Eromanga-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I don't know anyone by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're taking too long!\NHow long are you going to make me wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nyou've come to an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You gave up earlier, saying\Nyou can't even compete against her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you win,\NI'm sure she would be so frustrated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just imagining it makes me drool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, how are you going to win\Nagainst Muramasa? Do you have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll write like I normally do, and I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I can't do that, I can't make this dream\Ncome true in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I see, that's good.\NIt's an answer I like to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Specifically, I want to take\Nthat younger-sister novel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and have it fit the format\Nof Light-novel Tenkaichi Budoukai,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and rewrite it as a 60-page short story.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So you'll fight with a revised version of\Nthe love-letter novel that you defeated me with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Stop calling it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, that novel definitely has a chance to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,More like, that's the only thing you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I'm terrible with short stories.\NI could write long novels all day, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Time for training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's over 100 pages! How is this a short story?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Terrible architecture!\NStart with a super-interesting scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's too early for the heroine to go dere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Save the love confession\Nfor the climactic scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-Th-This heroine is somewhat like me, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So after all, you really do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DEADLINE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's getting pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It passes as a one-shot story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It can't be just passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I don't make it the best thing ever,\NI can't win against Muramasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's some determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, who is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, this attire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If speaking honestly,\Nto do the business I came here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanted to make\Nyour impression of me slightly better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As my editor said,\Nmost boys tend to like girls in uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Though I do question whether myself\Nin a uniform has any effect or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I would be happy if I drew your attention,\Neven just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wasn't asking about the outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What I want to ask\Nis the reason why you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune-kun.\NI came here to recommend surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You should become mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Become yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-No! What I meant was that you should become\N"a novelist writing just for me"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A novelist writing just for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Literally, you would write novels just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In return, I will pay you\Nmore than enough in rewards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How it sounds aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You said you were going\Nto crush my dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How does that connect\Nwith this proposition you just made?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune, you shouldn't ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all, you're a dumb little softie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you learn your enemy's situation,\Nyou'll be less likely to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yamashita-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yamada! It's Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nin Masamune-kun's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't call living next door to me\Nas "living together"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune-kun, you should listen to my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You should learn what my dream is,\Nthat will crush down yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you want to continue your current life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, with all that suggestive comments\Nand barging in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What the heck is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It looks like she's writing a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know. She suddenly\Nstarted writing mid-conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, you! What have you been writing—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you interrupt me, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm at a really good part right now.\NI'll be done shortly, so just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is she writing what she'll submit\Nto the Light-novel Tenkaichi Budoukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That can't be.\NThe deadline is in two days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then maybe it's the continuation\Nof Demon Sword that has been on hiatus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:10:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Nii-san{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's completely concentrating on writing,\Nso I don't think she'd notice anything we do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}lift up her skirt?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're a... You're such a... You're too hardcore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you interested in my underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, well, um....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-In the first place, this is all because
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,you suddenly started writing\Nthe continuation for Demon Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Demon Sword? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, you! That's enough of being airheaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Legend of the Illusionary Demon Sword.\NYou know of it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think I vaguely remember hearing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, that thing my editor\Nkeeps telling me to write.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, you don't even remember\Nthe titles of your own books?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Novels are things you write\Nso you can read it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If there's interesting text,\Nthe title doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I merely write novels.\NI don't know what happens after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Senpai, why did you become an author?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I debuted only because I went with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Your family won't hound you anymore\Neven if you write stories all day".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think I was convinced when I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, why did you start writing novels?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you want to read interesting novels, you can\Nbuy them at the bookstore and read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's because bookstores don't have novels
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,that I think are interesting\Nfrom the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I have no choice\Nbut to write them on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you don't have memories of reading a book\Nand finding it interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,you wouldn't even think about\Nwriting your own novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course, there was just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't read its continuation ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kouhai, out of 100, what score\Nwould you give the stories you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Same for me. An author's personal rating\Nshould always be 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, the first fan letter I ever read had said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"It was so interesting,\NI'd give it a 1,000,000 out of 100!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There was someone who would give\Na million-point rating
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,for my story that I gave a perfect hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I understood something\Nafter I became an author.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Authors are desperately creating novels\Nthat score a hundred points,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but the readers ever so easily\Ngive it a score of a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Depending on the person, they can obtain\Nmany books that are worth a million points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That is very unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A book for me is so rare to find,\Nand I can never read enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For a long, long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been hungry for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My dream is to write a novel\Nthat I can give a personal score of a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll write a novel that I feel is interesting\Nfrom the bottom of my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and I'll write as many as it takes\Nfor my own sake until I satiate my hunger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So that's what you look like when you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all, when you speak of dreams,\Nyou should laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I understand what your dream is now, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But why are you trying to crush our dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't remember getting in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because you started some boring\Nromantic-comedy project,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't write battle-based novels anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,See, didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You shouldn't haphazardly\Nlisten to her situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, we're going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yamamoto-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You really are dense, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The way you put it, Masamune won't\Nunderstand the most important part at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you want him to get it,\Nyou have to slam your real motive at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For me, the most interesting book\Nin the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...is what you write!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I can't forgive you\Nfor starting a different genre.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I love the battle-based novels that you write.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't stand not being able\Nto read them anymore! I just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have read every novel you have written.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've loved reading your works, back from\Nthe web-novels you wrote before your debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My novels have always been affected by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because you write novels that are so\Nheart-moving for me, I can continue to write!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was severely depressed when your\NSilverwolf of Reincarnation series ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What will happen afterwards to all\Nthe characters who I loved so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How could they have arrived\Nat a happy ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was all I could think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I'm not even the author.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To divert myself from the sadness,\NI wrote, and wrote, and wrote some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I impatiently thought,\N"Why won't Izumi-sensei release a new title?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, when I heard you submitted\Na proposal for a romantic-comedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I slam it down, I thought you would write\Nanother battle-based novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To stimulate you,\NI intentionally made you angry, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, after I did so,\NKagurazaka-san scolded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't realize you were in\Nsuch a dire situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In order to continue your current work, you\Nneed results and income as an author, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune-kun, give up that pointless dream,\Nand write novels just for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you could do that for me, I'll give you\Nall of the royalties I have gained to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you swear that you would be mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will protect you and your sister\Nfor the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Will you give me an answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Senpai, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't give him to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will never ever give him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was before you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I love him way more than you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,From the beginning, he's been mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Our dream is not pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Together. We made it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'd never lose against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Never, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I really appreciate the sentiments,\Nbut that's not high enough of a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm not gonna lose at all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's fight fair and square, and settle it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Senpai, you're one of my fans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't hate it when you haven't even read it.\NIt'd be a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because the new title
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,will be the best masterpiece\Nfrom "Izumi Masamune".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If it's not interesting, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can that be Izumi-sensei's manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yup. Dead last, barely made the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if Light-novel Tenkaichi Budoukai\Nbecomes a lively event.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will be rather lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right now, all the stories are pretty great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:54.96,EpNum,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frx31\fry357\move(240.974,130.489,337.081,-20.8,1,4427)\frz356.1}Steady School Notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:54.96,LeftSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frx31\fry357\frz356.1\move(79.148,408.533,176.668,326.755,6,4427)}Senju Muramasa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Though, there's one author\Nwho is way too laborious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.00,RightSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(505.974,124.711)}Bu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.00,CenterSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(430.36,227.111)}\NResults announcing in:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.00,CenterSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(433.186,270.489)}\N\N3 Minutes 3 Seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.00,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(559.679,124.711)}doukai
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.00,OnTop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(428.946,124.711)}Tenkaichi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:59.00,DefaultRightH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(317.293,124.711)}Light-novel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, three more minutes\Nuntil they announce the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This makes my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is your heart racing as much as\Nwhen you were forced
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,to read a love-letter right in front of\Nthe girl who gave it to you?
