Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, it's obvious if you read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M-Masamune-kun!
